{"tid":1304990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"重新眾焦五大訴求仲有呢個呀！！！","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:24:41.000Z","uid":69883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f39addbac8578507e38edfe0e5edefcf16feb3","tid":1304990,"uid":69883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:04:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好少開post, 開得唔好隨便屌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五、實行雙真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都知道依家我哋係要令香港有民主㗎可？<br />\n趁呢個時候大家冷靜返就快啲思考下我哋下一步應該點做<br />\n<br />\n[急! 反DQ] 香港政研會原來尋晚叫人去支持DQ書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303015</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n喺完咗登記選民大家覺得選舉仲有好遠嘅時候，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對家已經開始做緊嘢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋有我哋登記做選民，佢哋識入侵埋區議會，一步一步繼續侵蝕我哋民主</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而我哋連民主人權法個聯署都未過半數呀！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3dMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=88c8fa0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點同人講我哋香港人要民主呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求求大家冷靜啲，保持頭腦清醒咁去諗多啲有用嘅對策</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各自努力，加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"02c99f3c70d1c592244c78f12610216b047b1fa7","tid":1304990,"uid":69883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:07:03.000Z","msg":"一齊諗下萬一佢DQ書過咗，我哋可以做啲咩去抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de760c77ca62b173d8e46f98bd3248d1c025027","tid":1304990,"uid":69883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02c99f3c70d1c592244c78f12610216b047b1fa7","tid":1304990,"uid":69883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:07:03.000Z","msg":"一齊諗下萬一佢DQ書過咗，我哋可以做啲咩去抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"何況佢依家咁嘅態度根本想硬過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946eff808c27348e739c4d7bc41b67b2fc191de7","tid":1304990,"uid":83198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"一、<span style=\"color: gold;\">撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪 </span><br />\n二、<span style=\"color: gold;\">成立獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權 </span><br />\n三、<span style=\"color: gold;\">實行真雙普選 </span><br />\n四、撤回引渡條例修訂草案<br />\n五、撤回6.12暴動定義<br />\n六、要求永不實行「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、徹回「多功能監控系統」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n香港人 永不放棄<br />\n長期抗爭呀！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">請FOCUS返主線</span> <br />\n睇內文 要FACT CHECK <br />\n勿分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔好推膠post<br />\n整圖做文宣 air drop 俾其他市民<br />\n簽聯署<br />\n出活動要保護自己<br />\n唔好做沙包</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油！！！！！！